{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"body":"SPIKE RESOLVED (AC1): anthropic_cache_instructions=True caches the Agent(system_prompt=...) kwarg for rebar's exact call shape. Empirical: call1 cache_write_tokens=14416, call2 (different user instruction) cache_read_tokens=14416/write=0 — full cache hit on the stable system prompt. ⇒ Implementation = AnthropicModelSettings(anthropic_cache_instructions=True [+ anthropic_cache_tool_definitions for agentic]) gated to anthropic providers; NO user-message CachePoint, NO RunRequest content-list change (BLOCKER 2 dissolved). Usage fields: result.usage.cache_read_tokens / cache_write_tokens (usage is a PROPERTY now, not a method)."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1782545074667792001,"uuid":"4243d577-2e62-4734-ac5f-d26cddb9e3b9"}